CLOUD CHARACTERSTICS
-------------------------

*On-demand self-service â€“ You can get servers, storage, or apps whenever you need, without asking anyone.
*Broad network access â€“ You can access cloud services from anywhere using the internet (laptop, mobile, tablet).
*Resource pooling â€“ Cloud providers share their resources (servers, storage) among many users.
*Rapid elasticity (Scalability) â€“ You can easily increase or decrease resources (CPU, memory, storage) as per need.
*Measured service (Pay as you go) â€“ You only pay for what you actually use, like electricity or water.
*High availability & reliability â€“ Cloud is designed to be available 24/7 with backups.
*Security â€“ Data and applications are protected using encryption and access control.
ğŸ‘‰ In short: Cloud is flexible, scalable, available anytime, anywhere, and you pay only for what you use.
